data.description: Step inside of this West End home to be greeted by vaulted ceilings, floor-to-ceiling wood burning fireplace, and natural light from skylights! Warmth and elegance are seen in the numerous updates. New LVP flooring leads you through the main level. The expansive kitchen has ample counter space and cupboards with Quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Laundry is located on the main level with counter space and additional cupboard storage. The main level features three bedrooms to include the primary suite. Primary suite features a walk in closet and walk out to the back covered patio. Both main level bathrooms have been remodeled with tile and new fixtures. Most of the home has new paint. The lower level features a third living space, two bedrooms, and remodeled bathroom. Unfinished indoor work shop located in the lower level! Assumable VA loan @2.875% for qualified buyers.
